Installation & Usage

Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/yourusername/Game-Management-System.git

Open index.html in a browser.

Ensure a backend is set up for handling customer and game data if required.

Future Enhancements

Implement customer authentication and login system.

Add game purchase functionality.

Enhance UI with animations and improved user experience.

